## 1. Executive Summary & Product Vision

**Mecha Chameleon: Pig Protocol** is a fast-paced, web-based 3D multiplayer stealth and hide-and-seek game built using Three.js, Cannon-es physics, and Socket.IO. Players control low-poly "Cyber-Pig Soldiers" outfitted with active camouflage (optical cloaking), parkour abilities, dynamic pose transformation mechanics, and shoulder-mounted blaster weaponry.

The goal is to deliver an accessible browser gaming experience that pairs tactical stealth/disguise mechanics (inspired by prop hunt and stealth games) with high-mobility platforming and custom party matchmaking.

