## 4. User Interface (UI) & Experience (UX)

### 4.1 Lobby & Home Screen

* **3D Canvas Viewport:** Features a rotating preview mesh of the active Cyber-Pig Soldier with a side-mounted blaster on a retro grid.
* **Procedural Call-Sign Generator:** Auto-populates creative pig call-signs (e.g., `MisterPig102`, `BaconLord809`, `CaptainSwine404`) on every DOM load.
* **Party Management Dock:**
* **CREATE PARTY:** Instantly spins up a new server room instance and copies the room code to the HUD.
* **JOIN PARTY:** Text input bar supporting direct 4-letter room code entry.



### 4.2 In-Game HUD

* **Room Code Indicator:** Displays active session chamber key.
* **Ability Indicators:** Displays real-time Camouflage status and Perspective state (FPP/TPP).

